      </section>

      <!-- Process Section -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-primaryBlue mb-6 text-3xl font-semibold">Our Regulatory Service Process</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-primaryBlue text-xl font-semibold">Regulatory Assessment</h3>
              <p class="text-gray">
                We analyze your product and market goals to map out the appropriate regulatory pathway.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-primaryBlue text-xl font-semibold">Dossier Preparation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray">
                We compile and review CTD/ACTD, DMF, CEP, or medical device dossiers for global submissions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-primaryBlue text-xl font-semibold">Submission & Liaison</h3>
              <p class="text-gray">
                We submit dossiers to authorities like FDA, EMA, and CDSCO, managing queries and interactions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-primaryBlue text-xl font-semibold">Remediation & Compliance</h3>
              <p class="text-gray">We address regulatory deficiencies, prepare CAPAs, and ensure audit readiness.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="text-primary mr-4 text-2xl font-bold">5</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-primaryBlue text-xl font-semibold">Post-Approval Support</h3>
              <p class="text-gray">
                We manage variations, renewals, and lifecycle compliance to maintain market authorization.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Compliance & Guidelines -->
      <section class="bg-secondary-light2 mb-12 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-primaryBlue mb-6 text-3xl font-semibold">Compliance & Standards</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-primaryBlue mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Regulatory Bodies</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray list-inside list-disc">
              <li>FDA (U.S. Food and Drug Administration)</li>
              <li>EMA (European Medicines Agency)</li>
              <li>ICH (International Council for Harmonisation)</li>
              <li>CDSCO (Central Drugs Standard Control Organization)</li>
              <li>TGA, Health Canada, PMDA</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-primaryBlue mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Guidelines & Certifications</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray list-inside list-disc">
              <li>ICH Q1‚ÄìQ14</li>
              <li>CTD/ACTD Guidelines</li>
              <li>MDR-2017 (India)</li>
              <li>21 CFR Part 11</li>
              <li>ISO 13485 (Medical Devices)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-primaryBlue mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Applications & Industries</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray list-inside list-disc">
              <li>Pharmaceutical Manufacturing</li>
              <li>Biotechnology</li>
              <li>Medical Device Manufacturing</li>
              <li>Marketing Authorization Holders</li>
              <li>Generic & Biosimilar Producers</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Conclusion -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-primaryBlue mb-4 text-3xl font-semibold">Why Choose Our Regulatory Services?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Our CRO provides expert regulatory compliance and medical device registration services, ensuring seamless
          approvals across global markets. With comprehensive dossier preparation, strategic consulting, and
          post-approval support, we help you navigate complex regulations from FDA, EMA, CDSCO, and beyond. Choose us to
          accelerate your market entry and maintain compliance with confidence.
        </p>
